						               													<description>The players are relatives of aunt Luzie, who is soon going to die. Aim of the game is to inherit some of aunt Luzie's wealth.&amp;#10;To get to her money the players have a set of legacy-hunter-cards, from which 5 cards are drawn in the beginning. They are gifts for aunt Luzie. The inheritance cards are shuffled and placed in the middle of the board.&amp;#10;Every turn the players give aunt Luzie gifts like journeys or parties in form of the legacy-hunter-cards, which have a certain value from 1-6. Every player is allowed to give one card. In the 2nd phase another card can be placed to increase chances or to pick another category. After all players have placed cards aunt Luzie is moved around (dice) and according where she lands the player with the highest card(s) in that category inherits something.&amp;#10;The player with the most valuable inheritance cards in the end wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
